none.description:
{Base Benediction}

A hero is able to cast all spells with Basic proficiency.

Drains 10 'Power' daily and lasts until next week.

basic.description:
{Basic Benediction}

A hero is able to cast all spells with Basic proficiency.

Drains 2 'Power' daily and lasts until next week.

advanced.description:
{Advanced Benediction}

A hero is able to cast all spells with Advanced proficiency.

Drains 5 'Power' daily and lasts until next week.

expert.description:
{Expert Benediction}

A hero is able to cast all spells with Advanced proficiency.

Drains 8 'Power' daily and lasts until next week.
